OL,3,CMisinformation about new mosque by far-
OL,4,Cright groups used to 'whip up' tension
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent went
OL,7,Fto Dalton-in-Furness to meet the local
OL,8,FMuslim community
OL,10,FMisinformation about a new mosque is
OL,11,Fbeing shared by far-right groups to
OL,12,F'whip up tension' in the area, it has
OL,13,Fbeen claimed.
OL,15,FMembers of Barrow's Muslim community
OL,16,Fsay they are hurt by the crusade which
OL,17,Fis aiming to close the area's first
OL,18,Fmosque before it has even been built.
