OL,6,FThe building was granted planning
OL,7,Fpermission in 2022 without any
OL,8,Fcontroversy to provide a place of
OL,9,Fworship for around 50 Muslim doctors
OL,10,Fat the Furness General Hospital and
OL,11,Ftheir families.
OL,13,FBut after far right group Britain
OL,14,FFirst became involved just weeks ago
OL,15,Faround 70,000 people have now signed a
OL,16,Fpetition calling for that planning
OL,17,Fpermission to be revoked.
