OL,6,FThey have called it a 'super mosque'
OL,7,Fin the heart of the Lake District -
OL,8,Fdespite the fact it sits eight miles
OL,9,Ffrom the boundary of the national park.
OL,11,FCurrently Barrow does not have a
OL,12,Fmosque, with Muslims praying at the
OL,13,Flocal cricket club, and in a room in
OL,14,Fthe town's hospital.
OL,16,FTo visit a mosque they currently have
OL,17,Fto make a 100 mile round trip to
OL,18,FLancaster.
