OL,7,Fin Dalton-in-Furness, themselves,
OL,8,Fraising money to buy the land, and
OL,10,FMohammed Ramzan: "It's just the
OL,11,Fanimosity that's been caused, and the
OL,12,Fmisinformation that's been spread
OL,13,Faround the area.
OL,15,F"Some of those comments have upset me,
OL,16,Fthey've really upset me.
