OL,6,F"You think that these people that
OL,7,Fyou've shared bread with, you've gone
OL,8,Fout with, you've drank with, you've
OL,9,Fhad a life with an all of a sudden
OL,10,Fthese big bad Muslims are coming in,
OL,11,Fand they're not, we've already been
OL,12,Fhere.
OL,14,F"We're not big and bad, it (the
OL,15,Fmosque) is for people like myself, my
OL,16,Fwife, my children."
OL,18,FTensions have become so bad workers
OL,19,Fhave been hiding their faces, while
OL,20,Flocal suppliers initially pulled out
OL,21,Fof the site fearing reprisals.
