OL,6,FBut local residents say it is a small
OL,7,Fminority, supported by far right
OL,8,Fgroups, and right-leaning broadcaster
OL,9,FGB News, whipping up tensions.
OL,11,FThe controversy has forced Westmorland
OL,12,Fand Furness Council, to put out a
OL,13,Ffactsheet - correcting claims by GB
OL,14,FNews that an application for a
OL,15,Fchildren's home, which was dismissed
OL,16,Fby planners, was on a different site,
OL,17,Fand addressing concerns about a "mega
OL,18,Fmosque in the Lake District".
