OL,6,F"There has been a great deal of
OL,7,Fmisinformation spread to whip up local
OL,8,Ftensions around this application,"
OL,9,FCouncillor Matt Brereton said.
OL,11,F"The fact of the matter is the Furness
OL,12,Fpeninsula I know is a really welcoming
OL,13,Fplace.
OL,15,F"It's clear the misinformation being
OL,16,Fspread online is not being done by
OL,17,Flocal people because anyone who is
OL,18,Flocal knows that Dalton-in-Furness is
OL,19,Fabout a 30 minute drive away from the
OL,20,Fnearest boundary to the national park."
