OL,6,FRefugees who have made Barrow their
OL,7,Fhome say they have been shown nothing
OL,8,Fbut kindness.
OL,10,FFaizudin Ahmedi, 33, was a defence
OL,11,Flawyer in Afghanistan forced to flee
OL,12,Ffrom the Taliban, and now works at
OL,13,FBarrow's community garage.
OL,15,FHe was brought out of the country with
OL,16,Fhelp from the British government - and
OL,17,Fhas been granted settled status as a
OL,18,Frefugee.
