OL,6,F"The people in Barrow are very kind,"
OL,7,Fhe said. "We are very happy about the
OL,8,Fmosque."
OL,10,FHis boss, Thomas Henderson, supports
OL,11,Fthe mosque, and made a donation to
OL,12,Ftheir fundraising campaign.
OL,14,FThe Islamic centre still has to raise
OL,15,Fmore than a million pounds, but are
OL,16,Fconfident they'll reach that target
OL,17,Fand hope the mosque will be open at
